00:00:01,967 --> 00:00:05,515
Do you want any meat today. Mrs. Bird?
您今天要买点肉吗, Bird夫人?

2
00:00:06,042 --> 00:00:06,788
Yes, please.
是的, 我买一点.

3
00:00:07,705 --> 00:00:10,508
Do you want beef or lamb?
您要牛肉还是要羔羊肉?

4
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:12,941
Beef, please.
请给我牛肉.

5
00:00:13,918 --> 00:00:15,859
This lamb's very good.
这羊羔肉很好.

6
00:00:17,517 --> 00:00:20,877
