我喜欢羊羔肉, 可我丈夫不喜欢.

7
00:00:21,735 --> 00:00:23,617
What about some steak?
来点牛排吗?

8
00:00:24,548 --> 00:00:26,265
This is a nice piece.
这块很好.

9
00:00:27,333 --> 00:00:29,561
Give me that piece, please.
请给我那块吧.

10
00:00:30,495 --> 00:00:33,298
And a pound of mince, too.
再来一磅绞肉.

11
00:00:34,143 --> 00:00:37,470
Do you want a chicken, Mrs. Bird?
您要买只鸡吗, Bird夫人?

12
00:00:38,221 --> 00:00:39,323
They're very nice.
这些鸡很好.

13
00:00:40,491 --> 00:00:41,383
No, thank you.
不要了, 谢谢.

14
00:00:43,193 --> 00:00:45,274
My husband likes steak,
我丈夫喜欢牛排, 

15
00:00:45,751 --> 00:00:47,771
but he doesn't like chicken.
但他不喜欢鸡.

16
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:51,815
To tell you the truth, Mrs. Bird, 
说老实话, Bird夫人, 

17
